subject to a separate Runtime License Agreement (CLA/RLA.md).

The following components are NOT covered by Apache 2.0:

| Component | Type | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| meta_kernel_rules.dll | Coq compiled binary | 5 meta rules (open_completeness, fissure, foundation, recursion, observer) |
| constructive_rules.dll | Coq compiled binary | Constructive logic rules (duality check, ground chain, equivalence) |
